<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8089957>
    dc:description "FIGURE 15. Novius fumidus (Mulsant): a–d. darker variants (Tamil Nadu); e–g. male genitalia: e. tegmen, lateral view; f. tegmen, inner view; g. penis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8089957/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8089953>
    dc:description "FIGURE 14. Novius fumidus (Mulsant): a. head; b. prosternal intercoxal process; c. abdomen, male; d. abdominal postcoxal line; e. female genitalia; f. spermatheca; g–i. male genitalia: g. tegmen, lateral view; h. tegmen, inner view; i. penis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8089953/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8089959>
    dc:description "FIGURE 16. Novius fumidus (Mulsant): a, b. larva feeding on Icerya purchasi on casuarina; c–e. larval sibling cannibalism; f, g. larva on banana; h. pupa." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8089959/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8089963>
